<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background-color: #4CAF50;
      color: white;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }
    .confirmation-code {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #4CAF50;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: white;
      border: 2px solid #4CAF50;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .details {
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>🎉 Booking Confirmed!</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
      <p>Dear Customer,</p>
      
      <p>Thank you for your booking! Your reservation has been confirmed.</p>
      
      <div class="confirmation-code">
        <%= booking.confirmation_code %>
      </div>
      
      <div class="details">
        <h3>Booking Details:</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Confirmation Code:</strong> <%= booking.confirmation_code %></li>
          <li><strong>Seats Reserved:</strong> <%= booking.seats_reserved %></li>
          <li><strong>Total Price:</strong> <%= booking.total_price_currency %> <%= sprintf('%.2f', booking.total_price_amount) %></li>
          <li><strong>Email:</strong> <%= booking.email %></li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      
      <p>Please save this confirmation code. You'll need it to access your tickets.</p>
      
      <p>See you at the event! 🎟️</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
      <p>This is an automated email. Please do not reply.</p>
      <p>&copy; 2026 Ticketing System. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>